WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.120
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

00:00:01.160 --> 00:00:02.320
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

00:00:16.360 --> 00:00:17.360
Duang.

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:19.080
- Oh, Gam?
- Hi.

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:20.440
You're single, right?

00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:22.080
- Hey!
- Back off.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:23.760
Are you alright?

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:24.720
I simply...

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:26.760
don't like it when I can't
control my emotions.

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.960
I'm prepared to love you
with everything I have.

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:34.840
Why are you taking
me back to your place?

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:36.080
Are you having a mischievous plan?

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:38.040
Don't do this to me.

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:40.560
I can literally die.

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:44.710
You haven't even won me over.

00:00:44.750 --> 00:00:46.010
Are you really dying?

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.680
I'd better hurry, then.

00:01:09.190 --> 00:01:10.510
So funny, aren't you?

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:14.710
I never take matters about you lightly.

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:17.830
I'm serious, too.

00:01:18.150 --> 00:01:19.030
What's it going to be?

00:01:21.140 --> 00:01:22.789
You really want me to help you shower?

00:01:24.789 --> 00:01:27.270
Why the hell did you ask
if you thought I wouldn't let you?

00:01:29.660 --> 00:01:30.670
Well...

00:01:31.830 --> 00:01:32.610
See?

00:01:33.039 --> 00:01:33.800
I got you now.

00:01:34.090 --> 00:01:35.470
You were just pulling my leg.

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.320
Hey, I mean...

00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:38.610
Let me explain myself.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:40.729
I didn't expect you to let me.

00:01:40.770 --> 00:01:42.430
Then remember this.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.220
Never pull my leg.

00:01:48.630 --> 00:01:49.610
Well...

00:01:50.479 --> 00:01:51.720
Shall we take a shower?

00:01:51.759 --> 00:01:52.960
You missed your chance.

00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:04.950
Yes!

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.320
Next time, I won't fail!

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.400
I won't fail!

00:02:10.150 --> 00:02:11.950
Next time, just you wait!

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:33.120
♫I'm not leaving soon, so bear with me♫

00:02:33.660 --> 00:02:38.260
♫Wherever you are
is where I'll always be♫

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:42.160
♫Wherever you go,
I'll find you eventually♫

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:44.480
♫You may push me away, but I won't flee♫

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:47.520
♫Who would you love if it weren't me?♫

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:49.800
♫So, wanna make a deal, maybe?♫

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:52.200
♫Alright, alright, don't worry♫

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:54.480
♫Just date me first, take it easy♫

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:56.880
♫I'll be so cute you'll fall naturally♫

00:02:56.920 --> 00:02:59.200
♫No matter what,
you'll always run into me♫

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.600
♫Okay, okay, let it be♫

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:03.920
♫I know you're also into me,♫

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:06.440
♫Don't you feel the same? I can see♫

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:12.720
♫I'll keep on flirting,
don't try to avoid me♫

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:17.520
♫'Cause I won't stop
till you fall for me♫

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:22.079
♫I'll keep on flirting,
I won't stop, I guarantee♫

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:28.520
♫I'll love you hard,
and once you say yes, I'll set you free♫

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.240
- Hey.
- Hm?

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:39.370
I'm putting it here, okay?

00:03:39.660 --> 00:03:40.670
Mm.

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:43.440
Come sleep. I have a game tomorrow.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:45.250
Oh, you're right.

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:47.360
You're up against the Logistics guys.

00:03:48.130 --> 00:03:49.829
I'm sure you're going to smash them.

00:03:50.290 --> 00:03:52.450
That's because
I'll be cheering for you in the crowd!

00:03:57.290 --> 00:03:58.000
See?

00:04:01.270 --> 00:04:03.190
We each got ourselves a tattoo.

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.640
This feels like a dream.

00:04:06.270 --> 00:04:07.290
Thank you!

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:14.080
You sleep there.

00:04:14.570 --> 00:04:16.240
Don't cross the line.

00:04:16.910 --> 00:04:17.810
Understand?

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.440
Do you understand?

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.240
Yes, I do.

00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:31.790
I'm delighted to be sharing
the bed with you again.

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:34.000
It feels like I'm being attacked by you.

00:04:34.050 --> 00:04:35.270
My heart, I mean.

00:04:35.310 --> 00:04:37.270
It's totally gone!

00:04:37.710 --> 00:04:38.950
Dead already?

00:04:39.390 --> 00:04:40.400
Not really.

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.310
You're melting my heart.

00:04:42.350 --> 00:04:46.050
I'm feeling like melted chocolate!

00:04:49.390 --> 00:04:50.590
Sweet dreams.

00:05:00.330 --> 00:05:01.890
No, I must not cross the line.

00:05:02.310 --> 00:05:04.910
But staying on top of the line
should be fine, right?

00:05:11.630 --> 00:05:14.490
Once I'm done with class,
I'll rush there to support you.

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:20.260
Do promise me that
you won't get yourself hurt.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.080
Mm.

00:05:29.630 --> 00:05:30.910
Promise?

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.280
Promise me first.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:37.070
I promise you.

00:05:44.470 --> 00:05:46.130
I won't get hurt.

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.920
You've promised!

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:53.400
Is there anything you want?
I'll get it for you.

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:54.400
No.

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:01.090
Having you there is enough.

00:06:03.930 --> 00:06:05.500
Come give me a big hug!

00:06:14.670 --> 00:06:16.390
I'll be there to cheer you on!

00:06:21.470 --> 00:06:23.210
"Having you there is enough."

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:25.850
"Having you there is enough!"

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.680
Where should we sit?

00:07:09.400 --> 00:07:10.600
Is Qin here?

00:07:14.030 --> 00:07:15.150
Do you see him?

00:07:16.910 --> 00:07:17.800
No, I don't.

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:19.930
Gosh, you're so uniquely stupid.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:22.870
If you're in such a rush,
why didn't you come yesterday?

00:07:22.910 --> 00:07:24.000
Alright.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:26.420
If I could've booked a seat,
I'd have been here since yesterday.

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:29.530
When will Duang stop being madly in love?

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:31.870
After the end of the world, I bet.

00:07:37.850 --> 00:07:39.170
Woo-hoo!

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:46.000
Ready?

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:48.150
Three! Four!

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:50.320
Ready!

00:07:51.200 --> 00:07:52.620
There are cheerleaders, too?

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:54.720
Three and four!

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:56.610
Qin, you've got this!

00:07:56.760 --> 00:07:58.510
Qin, you're fantastic!

00:07:58.550 --> 00:08:00.110
Qin, you slay!

00:08:00.150 --> 00:08:01.150
Qin...

00:08:01.190 --> 00:08:03.190
You're so cute!

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:07.840
Woo!

00:08:07.880 --> 00:08:08.800
Gosh!

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:13.240
That's all you've got, girls?

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:15.840
You can't be cheering for Qin like we do.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:17.560
Just watch us.

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:20.520
Get ready!

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:21.880
So ready!

00:08:23.640 --> 00:08:25.320
Three! Four!

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:26.380
Bang!

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:28.840
On fire!

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:29.800
Slay!

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:30.440
Slay!

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:31.640
Slay!!

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.679
Slay, slay, slay, king!

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:36.480
Bet you can't top that.

00:08:36.740 --> 00:08:37.640
Duang.

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:38.640
Don't let them win the game.

00:08:38.679 --> 00:08:39.799
Give it your best shot!

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:41.919
I think I have to give it to them.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:44.920
The match is starting soon.

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:48.150
Athletes, please stand by
on the sidelines.

00:08:58.360 --> 00:08:59.680
There he is!

00:08:59.730 --> 00:09:01.330
Qin is here!

00:09:01.370 --> 00:09:03.190
- There he is!
- Yeah!

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.520
I know!

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.680
Qin!

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:12.960
Qin!!

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.660
Hey, Qin.

00:09:24.450 --> 00:09:25.670
Qin!

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.520
You've got this!

00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:32.960
You might as well bring
a telescope at this rate.

00:09:35.520 --> 00:09:37.280
If the athletes from both teams are ready,

00:09:37.320 --> 00:09:39.440
- please enter the stadium.
- Ready?

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.200
Go.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.200
Let's go.

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:43.990
They're calling.

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:50.160
Today's match is between

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:53.040
Blue Team from the Faculty of Logistics

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:57.320
and their opponent,
Red Team, from the College of Music.

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:08.440
Please compete with good sportsmanship.

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:10.880
Embrace the spirit of good sportsmanship,
winning or losing,

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:15.320
to foster friendship
among fellow students.

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:19.160
Qin!

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.360
Qin, you've got this!

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:21.910
I'm right here!

00:10:21.950 --> 00:10:22.960
Ah!

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.760
Qin, show them what you're made of!

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:26.200
Woo-hoo!

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:28.480
There.

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:31.240
It's these two.

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:44.640
The crowds from the College of Music
seem very lively.

00:10:52.040 --> 00:10:56.440
Red Team wins the tip-off
and secures possession.

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:04.260
Red Team
is passing the ball perfectly,

00:11:04.300 --> 00:11:06.480
and it finally ends up with No. 7,

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:10.920
who goes for a layup
and scores the first two points.

00:11:12.430 --> 00:11:16.640
Let's now look at
the counterattack from Blue Team.

00:11:16.840 --> 00:11:19.320
With this clear space,
No. 7 is jumping at the gap.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:21.940
There's our three-pointer! Bang! Bang!

00:11:21.980 --> 00:11:23.940
- Bro, that's not gonna work.
- Blue Team won't back down, either,

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:26.760
bouncing back with a three-pointer from No. 7.

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.680
Red Team makes it a tight game
with a two-point shot!

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:39.360
Wow, however, Red Team
responds instantly with a shot

00:11:39.400 --> 00:11:43.040
- that catches Red Team off guard.
- Man, what the hell?

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:45.160
No. 21 from Blue Team tries
to take a shot but misses.

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:47.520
The ball falls into the hands of No. 7,

00:11:47.560 --> 00:11:49.280
who makes a hook shot for two points!

00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:52.800
The whistle's blown,

00:11:52.840 --> 00:11:55.960
concluding the first quarter
with the score of 20:24.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.960
Blue Team is ahead by four points.

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:02.120
Let's see what plan Red Team has
to bounce back.

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:05.400
Play defensively
and conserve your energy for now, okay?

00:12:05.450 --> 00:12:08.250
As for you,
move fast and hold the center line.

00:12:08.470 --> 00:12:10.710
Push slowly, let Qin do the attack.

00:12:10.910 --> 00:12:12.070
You, get the ball to the teammate.

00:12:12.110 --> 00:12:14.130
You two, score at opposite ends.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:16.360
Let's move on to the second quarter

00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:18.400
with Red Team taking the first move.

00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:23.520
No. 23 goes up for a shot.

00:12:23.560 --> 00:12:25.640
There it goes. Two points scored.

00:12:27.800 --> 00:12:28.760
Boom!

00:12:31.270 --> 00:12:36.280
The momentum swings back
in Red Team's favor after No. 23 scores.

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:39.960
- Let's go.
- With Red Team's game plan,

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.880
Blue Team
is like deer in the headlights.

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:45.080
Gotta give it up for Red Team's offense,
especially from No. 23.

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:47.670
He shoots,
he passes the ball, you name it.

00:12:47.710 --> 00:12:51.360
Looks like Red Team has gotten
this match in the palm of their hand.

00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:53.490
They're the only team
to score at this moment.

00:12:53.800 --> 00:12:55.320
That's the end of the second quarter.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:59.080
Red Team has turned the game around.
They're now in the lead by eight points!

00:12:59.120 --> 00:12:59.990
Understood?

00:13:00.030 --> 00:13:02.050
Be aggressive and play strong.

00:13:02.090 --> 00:13:03.330
Don't be afraid of them.

00:13:03.670 --> 00:13:05.720
Alright. This is now the third quarter.

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:08.080
Let's see how this game plays out.

00:13:11.960 --> 00:13:14.360
Whoa, Blue Team
fought with physical strength

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:16.120
and scored.

00:13:23.560 --> 00:13:25.840
Holy moly, No. 7
continues with aggressive moves,

00:13:25.880 --> 00:13:29.000
pushing his way inside
and scoring once again.

00:13:30.090 --> 00:13:32.880
It seems like Blue Team is shifting
their game plan in the third quarter

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:35.720
to be more physical.

00:13:37.400 --> 00:13:40.120
Here comes
another scoring opportunity for Blue Team.

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:41.760
One push,

00:13:41.810 --> 00:13:44.590
and it's a layup. Two points.

00:13:44.630 --> 00:13:48.630
The Blue Team crowd
is certainly in a great mood.

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:53.640
Red Team, however, is not to be outdone

00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:55.520
They're still at it.

00:13:55.560 --> 00:13:59.160
The third quarter has been neck and neck.

00:14:03.880 --> 00:14:05.480
That's it for the third quarter.

00:14:06.010 --> 00:14:07.170
Take it easy. Same strategy.

00:14:07.210 --> 00:14:10.030
If you can't,
have PK help you advance the ball.

00:14:10.410 --> 00:14:12.530
Take the ball from them and score.

00:14:12.570 --> 00:14:14.630
Our game plan is fast-paced,
so we can do this.

00:14:15.110 --> 00:14:17.290
- Logistics!
- Come on, let's go for another quarter.

00:14:20.140 --> 00:14:21.170
One, two, three!

00:14:21.210 --> 00:14:22.610
Rhythm!

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.120
Alright, we're in the fourth quarter,
the final stretch.

00:14:27.160 --> 00:14:28.960
It's anyone's game at this point.

00:14:35.640 --> 00:14:37.960
Gotta say,
with how neck and neck the scores are,

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:40.180
no one has the upper hand here.

00:14:44.440 --> 00:14:45.880
No. 23 makes his way in,

00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:48.200
puts up a layup and scores.

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:50.080
Wow, what a beautiful shot.

00:14:50.520 --> 00:14:52.880
No. 7 from Red Team
perfectly faked and scored.

00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:54.560
And No. 7 from the other team...

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.840
Whoa!

00:14:57.330 --> 00:14:59.720
Things are fairly intense.

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:03.240
Right now, the two teams
keep taking turns being in the lead.

00:15:07.080 --> 00:15:09.200
It's such a nail-biting game we have.

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:11.720
We can't predict what comes next at all.

00:15:16.160 --> 00:15:16.800
Qin!

00:15:28.680 --> 00:15:31.040
It seems like
a minor accident has occurred.

00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:32.260
It's normal.

00:15:32.520 --> 00:15:33.170
Whoa!

00:15:33.210 --> 00:15:35.760
However, Blue Team
doesn't care in this final stretch.

00:15:35.800 --> 00:15:37.200
They're immediately retaliating.

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:40.920
Hey!

00:15:43.520 --> 00:15:46.280
Time is going down
until it's less than a minute left now.

00:15:46.320 --> 00:15:47.980
Every point counts.

00:15:48.400 --> 00:15:50.320
A Blue Team player fakes a pass

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:51.440
and shoots!

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:53.480
Bam, that's a three-pointer!

00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:56.670
Blue Team is now in the lead,

00:15:56.710 --> 00:15:58.320
which puts Red Team in real trouble.

00:15:58.670 --> 00:16:01.240
Here's the chance
for Red Team to counterattack.

00:16:01.280 --> 00:16:04.080
- Go, go, go.
- No. 23 takes the ball into his own hands.

00:16:05.950 --> 00:16:06.870
Keep going!

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:08.760
Give it a spin and take a leap!

00:16:17.490 --> 00:16:17.990
Hey!

00:16:18.030 --> 00:16:19.640
That's a shooting foul.

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:22.400
That was a dangerous play,
considering how aggressive it was.

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:25.480
You could say it was unsportsmanlike.

00:16:25.640 --> 00:16:26.600
Qin!

00:16:28.360 --> 00:16:29.480
You guys are so fucking aggressive!

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:30.960
Can't you just play fair?

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:31.880
Yeah!

00:16:32.490 --> 00:16:33.450
Come on! Ref!

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:35.020
Ref!

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:37.840
Two shots.

00:16:39.400 --> 00:16:42.800
Of course, Red Team
will get two free throws.

00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:54.480
Right now, there's only
23 seconds left on the clock.

00:16:54.520 --> 00:16:57.240
If Red Team can score
two free throws back-to-back,

00:16:57.280 --> 00:16:59.640
there will be no hope left for Blue Team.

00:16:59.680 --> 00:17:02.300
- Miss, miss, miss.
- Score, score, score.

00:17:02.340 --> 00:17:07.359
- Miss, miss, miss.
- Score, score, score.

00:17:14.119 --> 00:17:18.119
Both teams are now tied at 61.

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:20.839
If Red Team scores
this second free throw,

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:22.640
it'll be a big advantage for them.

00:17:23.040 --> 00:17:23.920
However, if they don't,

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:28.760
this will give Blue Team a chance
to respond with their final play.

00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:52.400
Whoa!

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:55.240
Wow, that's incredible!

00:18:55.280 --> 00:18:59.960
The match ends with a three-pointer
from Red Team's No. 23,

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:05.600
sealing the win,
with the score of 64:61.

00:19:22.510 --> 00:19:22.920
Damn.

00:19:22.960 --> 00:19:24.400
Even though we didn't win,

00:19:24.540 --> 00:19:25.660
that asshole got hurt.

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:27.280
- So satisfying.
- Yeah.

00:19:27.320 --> 00:19:28.640
I knocked him to the ground.

00:19:28.680 --> 00:19:29.880
- I saw that.
- Sheesh.

00:19:37.630 --> 00:19:38.600
Hey!

00:19:38.640 --> 00:19:39.320
Hey!

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:41.000
- Whoa...
- Duang!

00:19:41.520 --> 00:19:42.320
- Duang!
- Hey...

00:19:44.710 --> 00:19:45.750
What the fuck is wrong with you?

00:19:48.600 --> 00:19:49.680
Oh.

00:19:49.800 --> 00:19:51.800
He's got his guardian angel.

00:19:54.590 --> 00:19:55.480
Right.

00:19:55.520 --> 00:19:56.480
Bastard!

00:19:56.670 --> 00:19:57.590
- Hey!
- Duang...

00:19:58.570 --> 00:19:59.350
Bring it.

00:20:00.910 --> 00:20:01.790
Let him go

00:20:02.480 --> 00:20:03.560
and come with me.

00:20:04.320 --> 00:20:05.320
Listen to him.

00:20:09.120 --> 00:20:10.600
- Duang, Duang...
- Whoa, whoa, whoa...

00:20:19.310 --> 00:20:21.430
Sheesh. Taking care of each other?

00:20:21.690 --> 00:20:22.670
Limping, huh?

00:20:22.710 --> 00:20:23.670
Let's just go.

00:20:43.150 --> 00:20:44.160
Go on without me.

00:20:44.600 --> 00:20:45.760
Alright, fine.

00:20:46.050 --> 00:20:47.310
Duang, take care of Qin, okay?

00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:49.270
Let's go, guys.

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:50.120
Bye-bye.

00:20:50.630 --> 00:20:51.510
See you.

00:21:22.280 --> 00:21:23.440
Why did you do that?

00:21:26.840 --> 00:21:28.840
You told me you wouldn't get hurt.

00:21:32.180 --> 00:21:33.630
I already did.

00:21:33.940 --> 00:21:34.950
It already happened.

00:21:35.810 --> 00:21:37.230
There's nothing either of us could do.

00:21:37.500 --> 00:21:39.080
Are you going to be
the only one getting hurt?

00:21:39.240 --> 00:21:40.250
Duang.

00:21:41.270 --> 00:21:42.390
Get a grip.

00:21:46.760 --> 00:21:48.550
How could I not be worried?

00:21:51.840 --> 00:21:53.840
I'm as hurt as you are.

00:21:55.850 --> 00:21:57.250
It's even worse for me, too.

00:22:04.760 --> 00:22:06.480
How would that even be possible?

00:22:53.910 --> 00:22:55.150
I'm sorry.

00:22:57.150 --> 00:22:58.160
It was my fault

00:22:58.910 --> 00:23:00.370
that I couldn't keep my promise.

00:23:19.170 --> 00:23:21.170
I told you I wouldn't get hurt,

00:23:22.910 --> 00:23:24.310
but I did.

00:23:27.350 --> 00:23:28.550
Hey...

00:23:30.490 --> 00:23:31.690
I'm sorry.

00:23:33.920 --> 00:23:34.920
Forgive me.

00:23:37.910 --> 00:23:38.910
Mm.

00:23:39.080 --> 00:23:40.280
I'm sorry, too.

00:23:44.080 --> 00:23:45.480
Thank you

00:23:46.910 --> 00:23:48.710
for taking such good care of me.

00:24:31.730 --> 00:24:32.630
See?

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:36.090
I told you not to move too much.

00:24:37.200 --> 00:24:38.330
You're scolding me for this?

00:24:38.840 --> 00:24:40.040
You're as fierce as a dog.

00:24:41.000 --> 00:24:42.880
It could get worse, okay?

00:24:48.320 --> 00:24:49.320
Are you still mad?

00:24:50.780 --> 00:24:52.180
I'm not mad at you,

00:24:53.500 --> 00:24:54.900
but at those who hurt you.

00:24:58.000 --> 00:24:59.010
I'm sorry.

00:24:59.200 --> 00:25:00.040
I'm sorry.

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:00.920
I'm sorry.

00:25:00.960 --> 00:25:01.960
I'm sorry.

00:25:03.080 --> 00:25:04.690
Stop with that tone of voice.

00:25:05.720 --> 00:25:07.620
You've already got my heart.

00:25:09.480 --> 00:25:11.570
This time, I'm going to die for real.

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:15.200
You forgive me too easily.

00:25:15.800 --> 00:25:17.670
You know me too well.

00:25:23.120 --> 00:25:24.040
Well...

00:25:29.840 --> 00:25:31.240
What did you just say?

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:33.780
I'm hungry.

00:25:34.720 --> 00:25:35.400
Huh?!

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:36.910
I'm hungry right now.

00:25:37.110 --> 00:25:38.590
Oh, come on!

00:25:39.780 --> 00:25:41.330
My heart almost sank.

00:25:42.120 --> 00:25:44.120
I thought you called me in that manner.

00:25:46.070 --> 00:25:48.310
In this economy,

00:25:48.350 --> 00:25:51.760
nothing beats
two packs of rice for ten baht.

00:25:52.010 --> 00:25:53.200
Check this out.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:55.240
It's stir-fried whiteleg shrimp
with garlic.

00:25:55.480 --> 00:25:57.880
It's rare to find this dish at this price.

00:25:58.640 --> 00:26:00.120
Am I going to die if I eat this?

00:26:02.080 --> 00:26:05.240
Don't be so pessimistic, alright?

00:26:05.410 --> 00:26:07.280
This is who I am.

00:26:08.120 --> 00:26:10.280
I'm good at cooking, you know?

00:26:13.920 --> 00:26:14.680
Here.

00:26:15.370 --> 00:26:16.350
All done.

00:26:16.590 --> 00:26:17.840
Eat up if you can.

00:26:17.880 --> 00:26:20.680
If you can't, throw it away!

00:26:28.570 --> 00:26:29.230
Nom!

00:26:29.270 --> 00:26:29.760
Ready?

00:26:29.800 --> 00:26:30.960
Nom!

00:26:32.240 --> 00:26:33.700
You're spoiling me.

00:26:34.000 --> 00:26:34.960
No need to feed me.

00:26:35.180 --> 00:26:36.390
My hands are fine.

00:26:36.840 --> 00:26:37.840
My foot isn't.

00:26:39.540 --> 00:26:41.480
I want to take care of you.

00:26:41.640 --> 00:26:43.910
I want you to get plenty of rest,

00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:46.910
eat your favorite food,
and do whatever you want.

00:26:47.350 --> 00:26:48.010
Huh?

00:26:48.240 --> 00:26:49.280
What does that have to do with this?

00:26:50.640 --> 00:26:51.800
It's with this!

00:26:54.600 --> 00:26:56.840
All that talk, same old meaning.

00:26:57.630 --> 00:26:58.870
Come on, now.

00:26:58.910 --> 00:26:59.750
Whatever.

00:26:59.790 --> 00:27:00.530
Here.

00:27:00.570 --> 00:27:01.900
♫Qin, nom, nom♫

00:27:02.080 --> 00:27:03.680
♫Qin, you're a good boy♫

00:27:03.720 --> 00:27:05.330
♫Good boy, nom, nom♫

00:27:05.370 --> 00:27:06.780
♫Nom, nom, good job!♫

00:27:06.960 --> 00:27:09.160
Nom!

00:27:09.590 --> 00:27:12.180
Nom!

00:27:15.540 --> 00:27:16.910
It's as simple as that.

00:27:17.610 --> 00:27:19.130
All I have is you.

00:27:19.560 --> 00:27:21.680
Spoiling you this much
means nothing to me.

00:27:29.400 --> 00:27:30.900
Can you do me a favor?

00:27:33.340 --> 00:27:34.120
Do tell.

00:27:35.120 --> 00:27:36.520
I want to get back
to dance practice already.

00:27:37.990 --> 00:27:40.020
I've dedicated
too much time to basketball.

00:27:40.440 --> 00:27:42.180
But your foot is hurt.

00:27:42.480 --> 00:27:44.350
Just let bygones be bygones.

00:27:45.490 --> 00:27:47.490
Another big event
is just around the corner, Duang.

00:27:48.060 --> 00:27:48.880
Hey!

00:27:48.920 --> 00:27:49.860
You're right!

00:27:49.900 --> 00:27:51.340
We've only got a few days left!

00:27:51.380 --> 00:27:52.280
Ah!

00:27:52.320 --> 00:27:54.150
What do we do?!

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:56.240
What should we do?

00:28:19.840 --> 00:28:21.110
Looking for someone?

00:28:22.910 --> 00:28:24.240
Come on.

00:28:24.630 --> 00:28:25.500
You already know that.

00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:26.910
You're hooked?

00:28:27.410 --> 00:28:28.850
You rarely go for the same person.

00:28:30.910 --> 00:28:32.480
Everything happens
for a reason, doesn't it?

00:28:33.680 --> 00:28:35.440
If you think this is your moment,

00:28:35.720 --> 00:28:37.470
it'll always be yours.

00:28:39.190 --> 00:28:40.910
You sound like a fortune teller.

00:28:41.720 --> 00:28:42.910
You believe in one?

00:28:43.280 --> 00:28:44.280
Nuts.

00:28:44.510 --> 00:28:45.670
Who would?

00:28:45.930 --> 00:28:47.460
I don't really mind

00:28:47.760 --> 00:28:48.930
if I get rejected.

00:28:54.590 --> 00:28:56.310
I do believe things happen
for a reason, though.

00:29:05.160 --> 00:29:06.560
Then tonight is my moment.

00:29:26.240 --> 00:29:28.920
You're the most beautiful person here.

00:29:30.400 --> 00:29:31.400
Am I?

00:29:31.640 --> 00:29:32.640
Yeah.

00:29:32.740 --> 00:29:33.740
You are.

00:29:36.330 --> 00:29:37.340
And...

00:29:38.390 --> 00:29:39.400
Hm?

00:29:41.910 --> 00:29:43.720
You're only here to compliment me?

00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:48.350
What should I do?

00:29:50.280 --> 00:29:52.360
I'm not the type to say one thing
and mean another.

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:57.960
Say it.

00:30:03.240 --> 00:30:04.520
Say it.

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:10.680
Well...

00:30:10.720 --> 00:30:12.280
You have me tonight.

00:30:21.350 --> 00:30:22.500
Bottoms up.

00:32:38.370 --> 00:32:39.090
Fantastic.

00:32:45.680 --> 00:32:47.280
I've heard that your leg got hurt.

00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:49.160
Will you be able to dance?

00:32:53.880 --> 00:32:56.680
Are you pretending
because you're afraid you'll lose?

00:32:57.120 --> 00:32:59.540
I usually don't like competition.

00:33:00.240 --> 00:33:01.440
But with you guys,

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:03.000
why should we give up?

00:33:22.540 --> 00:33:23.960
- Bye.
- Goodbye.

00:33:34.510 --> 00:33:35.740
Okay.

00:33:36.120 --> 00:33:39.120
From what I've seen,
things have gone pretty well.

00:33:39.430 --> 00:33:42.230
It's just that your accents
need a bit more work.

00:34:00.090 --> 00:34:01.170
How are you doing, Qin?

00:34:01.320 --> 00:34:02.600
Your foot, will it heal in time?

00:34:04.830 --> 00:34:05.640
It will.

00:34:05.680 --> 00:34:06.880
The pain is mostly gone.

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:09.489
Are you hurt?

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:12.159
I want to take the pain for you.

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:13.920
Ridiculous.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:18.639
♫But this isn't a forever goodbye♫

00:34:19.920 --> 00:34:20.679
That's great.

00:34:20.840 --> 00:34:23.449
I'm not worried about your dancing.

00:34:23.489 --> 00:34:24.570
You'd better heal up in time.

00:34:24.920 --> 00:34:28.120
I'd like to add something.

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:30.909
For your singing technique,

00:34:31.110 --> 00:34:34.040
you've already nailed it,
and I'm not worried about that.

00:34:34.080 --> 00:34:35.080
But...

00:34:35.659 --> 00:34:37.650
The emotion

00:34:37.760 --> 00:34:39.960
isn't there yet.

00:34:41.239 --> 00:34:42.250
I'm sorry?

00:34:43.040 --> 00:34:44.840
I'm not sure about it myself,

00:34:44.880 --> 00:34:47.920
as I'm not an expert.

00:34:48.280 --> 00:34:49.280
How about this?

00:34:49.469 --> 00:34:53.400
Look at how professional singers
convey their emotions.

00:34:53.440 --> 00:34:55.040
Learn from them and adapt it, okay?

00:34:55.080 --> 00:34:57.150
I'll sing this first part.

00:34:57.190 --> 00:34:59.180
And I'll follow it up with this.

00:35:07.600 --> 00:35:10.540
♫No matter how far...♫

00:35:10.760 --> 00:35:13.640
♫No matter how far...♫

00:35:13.880 --> 00:35:17.280
♫Or how long it takes♫

00:35:17.440 --> 00:35:20.720
♫Or how long it takes♫

00:35:24.870 --> 00:35:25.720
One more time?

00:35:32.160 --> 00:35:33.640
Wow!

00:35:33.680 --> 00:35:34.930
Wow

00:35:35.460 --> 00:35:36.910
Oh, whoa!

00:35:37.400 --> 00:35:41.000
Wow!

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:16.400
Hey.

00:36:18.720 --> 00:36:23.280
[My Stupid-ass Bro]

00:36:23.440 --> 00:36:24.640
Hello, Funan?

00:36:26.330 --> 00:36:27.160
Right.

00:36:27.880 --> 00:36:29.320
Mami says she's missing you.

00:36:30.350 --> 00:36:32.080
You rarely reply to the family group chat.

00:36:32.400 --> 00:36:33.240
Well...

00:36:33.440 --> 00:36:35.840
Tell her that I also miss her,

00:36:36.180 --> 00:36:37.320
but the ceremony is soon.

00:36:37.360 --> 00:36:38.680
Your dance performance?

00:36:38.910 --> 00:36:39.910
When is it?

00:36:42.640 --> 00:36:43.720
Why do you need to know about it?

00:36:43.910 --> 00:36:44.710
What?

00:36:45.750 --> 00:36:47.080
I'll be there to see you.

00:36:47.660 --> 00:36:48.360
Why?

00:36:48.400 --> 00:36:49.890
You're afraid
your friends will make fun of you?

00:36:50.060 --> 00:36:51.560
My friends might,

00:36:52.330 --> 00:36:53.560
but my rivals

00:36:54.240 --> 00:36:55.480
certainly will.

00:36:55.790 --> 00:36:57.590
Come on. What's there to be afraid of?

00:36:57.800 --> 00:36:59.480
You're such a chicken.

00:36:59.640 --> 00:37:00.500
Gosh, Funan.

00:37:00.720 --> 00:37:02.320
Don't come if that's what you want to say.

00:37:02.360 --> 00:37:04.160
I'll have my friend
send you the video of the dance.

00:37:05.400 --> 00:37:06.360
Are you going to tell me or not?

00:37:07.390 --> 00:37:08.560
You won't be at work?

00:37:08.600 --> 00:37:10.000
Lately, I'm feeling a bit lazy.

00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:12.440
I'll be there, okay?

00:37:12.720 --> 00:37:14.000
Fine, fine.

00:37:14.480 --> 00:37:15.880
Come if you want.

00:37:16.160 --> 00:37:17.860
But don't tell Mami and Dad, okay?

00:37:18.350 --> 00:37:20.660
The run-through is tomorrow.
The ceremony is the day after.

00:37:20.840 --> 00:37:21.690
Okay.

00:37:22.390 --> 00:37:23.870
Bye, Funan.

00:37:34.560 --> 00:37:35.430
Hey!

00:37:35.810 --> 00:37:36.910
- You like this song?!
- Today...

00:37:37.160 --> 00:37:38.170
It's also my favorite.

00:37:38.350 --> 00:37:39.940
- There's this new song I've just written.
- Mm.

00:37:40.120 --> 00:37:41.120
It's got great vibes.

00:37:41.320 --> 00:37:43.320
And I'd like you all to hear it.

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:46.480
I hope you like it.

00:38:04.480 --> 00:38:10.080
♫Do you think I'm good enough for you?♫

00:38:10.690 --> 00:38:18.210
♫Do I look like someone from your dreams?♫

00:38:19.930 --> 00:38:25.530
♫If you knew something about me♫

00:38:26.230 --> 00:38:30.000
♫And saw something,♫

00:38:30.040 --> 00:38:33.840
♫I wonder how disappointed you'd be♫

00:38:34.960 --> 00:38:39.960
♫I want you to know that
no matter how things change,♫

00:38:42.760 --> 00:38:48.570
♫My heart will always remain the same♫

00:38:49.370 --> 00:38:53.360
♫Would you still love me?♫

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:57.960
♫Could you accept me for who I am♫

00:38:58.120 --> 00:39:04.120
♫If I were just a nobody
who couldn't live up to your dreams?♫

00:39:04.840 --> 00:39:08.560
♫Could you still love me?♫

00:39:08.600 --> 00:39:13.480
♫Would I be the one you want♫

00:39:13.520 --> 00:39:19.360
♫If all I have is a heart that wants you?♫

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:23.920
♫Can you love me for my heart?♫

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:40.810
I'm hungry.

00:39:41.340 --> 00:39:42.180
Uh...

00:39:44.480 --> 00:39:45.940
I just ordered KFC, actually.

00:39:46.280 --> 00:39:47.440
It should arrive soon.

00:39:47.480 --> 00:39:48.480
Sit tight, okay?

00:39:59.600 --> 00:40:00.750
- Here it is.
- Give it here.

00:40:00.790 --> 00:40:02.130
Uh, no.

00:40:02.170 --> 00:40:03.210
I'll unpack it for you.

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:04.730
Go wash your hands.

00:40:04.920 --> 00:40:06.000
I'll unpack it myself.

00:40:43.760 --> 00:40:44.900
Slowly.

00:40:45.810 --> 00:40:47.120
You enjoy Wingz Zabb this much?

00:40:47.350 --> 00:40:48.120
Mm!

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:49.450
I do.

00:40:50.880 --> 00:40:52.440
What about you? Do you?

00:40:52.680 --> 00:40:53.680
Mm.

00:40:53.960 --> 00:40:54.970
It's alright.

00:40:55.800 --> 00:40:56.810
And...

00:40:59.200 --> 00:41:00.210
Between

00:41:00.640 --> 00:41:01.850
Wingz Zabb

00:41:02.090 --> 00:41:03.080
and me,

00:41:03.120 --> 00:41:04.240
which do you prefer?

00:41:07.880 --> 00:41:09.160
I prefer...

00:41:10.080 --> 00:41:11.080
Wingz Zabb.

00:41:15.280 --> 00:41:17.240
I'm just as spicy, you know?

00:41:26.360 --> 00:41:27.650
Watch it.

00:41:27.690 --> 00:41:28.910
You're making a mess.

00:41:30.580 --> 00:41:31.930
How exactly?

00:41:32.500 --> 00:41:33.500
This?

00:41:52.940 --> 00:41:54.160
Oh, hey...

00:41:54.400 --> 00:41:56.510
Tinn asked us to fill out the form again.

00:41:58.680 --> 00:42:00.320
A team name is required this time around.

00:42:01.800 --> 00:42:02.800
Think of one.

00:42:02.840 --> 00:42:04.200
You have better taste than I do.

00:42:04.390 --> 00:42:06.600
All I can think of are cringey names, like

00:42:06.720 --> 00:42:09.720
"GodLike007," "Sigmaboys," and stuff.

00:42:10.640 --> 00:42:12.240
I'm not the only one on this team.

00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:15.520
We'll think of one together.

00:42:21.270 --> 00:42:22.580
How about

00:42:23.640 --> 00:42:24.760
this team name?

00:42:26.070 --> 00:42:27.170
How about "Duang & Qin"?

00:42:28.200 --> 00:42:29.200
No.

00:42:30.520 --> 00:42:31.530
I want a name that is

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:33.270
unique,

00:42:33.530 --> 00:42:34.530
just like you.

00:42:35.750 --> 00:42:36.760
What?

00:42:37.600 --> 00:42:39.800
I was taken aback when you said that word.

00:42:40.040 --> 00:42:41.930
Are you referring to what Pae said?

00:42:42.560 --> 00:42:43.640
What do you mean?

00:42:45.680 --> 00:42:46.400
Nothing.

00:42:47.290 --> 00:42:48.660
Well...

00:42:54.880 --> 00:42:55.760
Here.

00:42:56.000 --> 00:42:57.000
This.

00:42:57.540 --> 00:42:59.270
It hurts less to call myself out.

00:42:59.400 --> 00:43:01.600
[Team name]

00:43:03.000 --> 00:43:04.640
You still think you're not the best?

00:43:05.850 --> 00:43:06.860
Mm.

00:43:07.770 --> 00:43:09.770
That's what everyone around me tells me.

00:43:11.270 --> 00:43:13.230
It's also based on the name of a song.

00:43:28.840 --> 00:43:31.360
[Team name]

00:43:31.480 --> 00:43:32.420
Whoa!

00:43:33.520 --> 00:43:35.290
